  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1102">
<l>piṇikku maruntu piṟama ṉaṇiyiḻai</l>
<l>taṉṉōykkut tāṉē maruntu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The remedy for a disease is always something different (from it); but for the disease caused by this jewelled maid, she is herself the cure.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
